query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow') AND t1.name IN ('boolean',
'c#',
'doctrine',
'firefox',
'group-by',
'ios5',
'php',
'scala',
'selenium-webdriver',
'stl',
'webkit',
'xamarin.forms',
'xcode',
'youtube')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Explainer',
'Investor',
'Mortarboard',
'Steward',
'Tag Editor')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
